snippet.title: TOTSUGEKI 64 [PLAY AS MAY IN SM64]
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD: https://romhacking.com/hack/TOTSUGEKI-64
Github Repo: https://github.com/spktk/TOTSUGEKI64

PLAY AS MAY FROM GUILTY GEAR IN SM64! BUT LIKE ACTUALLY IN SM64! 
Just in time for May's canonical bday! Wowie!

Built off of the code I wrote for The Disaster of Brainrot series, but with a brand new updated May model, additional control options for console players, and a couple of secrets to find. (Console Compat confirmation soon)

All of my rom hacks: https://romhacking.com/user/spk
Twitter: https://twitter.com/spktkTV
